<p>GigaCheck implements two distinct task-specific models that share a comm=
on foundation:</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Classification Model</strong>: Document-level detection using L=
oRA-adapted Mistral-7B with a classification head</li>
<li><strong>Detection Model</strong>: Character-level span detection using =
Mistral-7B with DETR encoder-decoder architecture</li>
</ol>
<p>Both models are implemented in the <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5=
] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidde=
n after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">MistralAIDetectorForSequenceClassifica=
tion</code> class, which can operate in classification-only mode or with fu=
ll detection capabilities enabled.</p>
