<p>Loss computation differs between classification and detection modes:</p>
<p><strong>Classification Loss:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Uses <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] t=
ext-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#4848=
48]/30">CrossEntropyLoss</code> with optional class weights</li>
<li>Computed between <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py=
-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden da=
rk:bg-[#484848]/30">pooled_logits</code> and <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[=
#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] befor=
e:hidden after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">labels</code></li>
<li>Class weights can be specified via <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e=
5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidd=
en after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">ce_weights</code> parameter</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Detection Loss:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Computed by <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5] px-[0.25rem] py-[0.2=
0rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden after:hidden dark:bg=
-[#484848]/30">SetCriterion</code> (DETR loss function)</li>
<li>Includes multiple components: classification loss, bounding box loss, G=
IoU loss</li>
<li>Weighted and summed according to <code class=3D"rounded-sm bg-[#e5e5e5]=
 px-[0.25rem] py-[0.20rem] text-xs font-normal leading-[15px] before:hidden=
 after:hidden dark:bg-[#484848]/30">weight_dict</code></li>
<li>Returns both total loss and individual loss components</li>
</ul>
